Author: buddyflies
Text: That’s exactly how it is. Nobody understands unless they’ve felt it and I would never wish this on anyone. It just sucks and I truly believe we would never encourage this behaviour in anyone we only want a safe space to express ourselves. And I really do love everyone, if anybody sees this and is too scared to post please please please message one of us. Something I truly believe we have in common is that we care about others. I’m here for everyone

Author: Anavosa
Text: This made me tear up, damn pms haha. This is beautiful, fam. We aren’t alone. We have each other. And though we may be strangers, we are still part of a family. I love you all too. You’ve been so supportive and I can’t thank you all enough
